column5: I don,t post often,not much to say, too busy fishing.A couple of my better fish from this year.
Great fish and pics Double L!!!
Congrats Larry! You did real good. Some beauty fish there for sure.....and the palm trees are nothing to be sneezed at either.  Thanks for posting.
Those are some nice fish. congrats on a good year.
Nice fish larry great job !!!!!...hope you do as well or better for 08...
Some real beauts there LL.  Happy fishing on 08 to ya.
Some real beauties there!!! Didn't know they had muskie where palm trees grew....LOL.  Thanks for posting the pics.
Thanks guys , next year I'll just have to try harder(even fish more than I do now)
You don't have to try too hard, you're already one of the masters here.
